  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your Twisted Chakra creates a construct shield of chakra to protect you from incoming attacks without your input. As a Bonus Action, by spending 10 Twisted Chakra, you gain 30 Twisted Shields for the next minute. Twisted Shields take damage in place of your temporary hit points for its duration.</p><p>At the beginning of each of your turns, you can choose to spend Twisted Chakra to repair your Twisted Shields. For each Twisted Chakra you spend, you regain 3 Twisted Shields.</p>",
